snippet.title: Infected Shelter - Early Access Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Infected Shelter hits Steam Early Access on May 8th 2019!

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/926390/Infected_Shelter/
Subscribe to our mailing list: http://infectedshelter.com

Thank you for your support!
